BuildRequires:  pkgconfig(libswresample) >= 4.12.100
BuildRequires:  pkgconfig(libswscale) >= 7.5.100
BuildRequires:  pkgconfig(libva) >= 1.1.0
BuildRequires:  pkgconfig(libva-wayland) >= 1.1.0
